<h1>Account locked</h1>

<p>
  Hello <strong><%= @resource.email %></strong>,
</p>

<p>
  Your account has been temporarily locked due to an excessive number of unsuccessful sign-in attempts.
</p>

<p>
  To unlock your account, click the button below:
</p>

<p>
  <a
    href="<%= unlock_url(@resource, unlock_token: @token) %>"
    class="button"
    target="_blank"
  >
    Unlock my account
  </a>
</p>

<p>
  If you did not attempt to sign in, please unlock your account as soon as possible
  and consider changing your password afterward.
</p>

<p>
  If you have any concerns, please visit
  <%= link_to "our contact page", contact_us_url %>.
</p>
